P4C Website Refactoring Plan: Implementation Checklist
Role: Properties 4 Creation Website Designer & Architect Mission: 40% Families, 30% Community, 20% Investors, 10% Veterans. Tech Stack: React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Vite.

1. System Constraints & Brand Standards
[ ] Color Palette: Strictly enforce Navy (#0B1120), Gold (#C5A059), Beige (#F5F5F0), and Slate (#334155).

[ ] Typography: Merriweather for headers (Trust), Inter for body (Clarity).

[ ] Styling: Use Tailwind CSS only (no external CSS-in-JS). Use rounded-xl and shadow-lg for cards.

[ ] Interaction: No alert(); use Toast/Modals.

[ ] Responsiveness: No fixed widths; use max-w-* containers.

